---
import Section from "../ui/Section.astro";
import profilePortrait from "../../assets/cracovia.png";
---

<Section
  id="profile"
  number="01"
  titleEs="Perfil"
  titleEn="Profile"
  subtitleEs="Quien soy, lo que hago y lo que he hecho."
  subtitleEn="Who I am, what I do, and what I have done."
>

  <div slot="aside" class="mt-6 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5">
    <div class="aspect-[2/3] w-full">
      <img
        src={profilePortrait.src}
        alt="Retrato de Jose Luis Aguilar"
        class="h-full w-full object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/4 p-6">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-zinc-400">
        <span data-lang="es">Quien soy</span>
        <span data-lang="en">Who I am</span>
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base text-zinc-300" data-lang="es">
        Soy Jose Luis Aguilar, desarrollador Full-Stack con origen en la automatizacion
        industrial y programación de PLC's. Actualmente lidero SMART AGRO en Smart Fénix, integrando sensorizacion IoT,
        despliegue de servidores y visualizacion de datos en una plataforma propia.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base text-zinc-300" data-lang="en">
        I am Jose Luis Aguilar, a Full-Stack and IoT developer with industrial automation roots.
        I currently lead SMART AGRO at Smart Fenix, integrating IoT sensing, server deployments,
        and data visualization in a proprietary platform.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-zinc-500">
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1">Inglés avanzado</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1">Carnet y vehiculo propio</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1">Disponibilidad total para traslado y viajes</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/4 p-6">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-zinc-400">
        <span data-lang="es">Que hago</span>
        <span data-lang="en">What I do</span>
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base text-zinc-300" data-lang="es">
        Trabajo a diario con Python y Java en backend, React y Astro en frontend, SQL, Postgre e
        InfluxDB para datos, y Grafana para observabilidad. Tambien me encargo de despliegues en docker y vercel
        y automatizacion en Linux y el mantinimiento de servidores.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base text-zinc-300" data-lang="en">
        I work daily with Python and Java on the backend, React and Angular on the frontend,
        SQL and InfluxDB for data, and Grafana for observability. I also handle deployments
        and automation on Linux.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-zinc-500">
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1">Python</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1">Java</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1">React</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1">Angular</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1">SQL</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1">InfluxDB</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1">Grafana</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1">Linux</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/4 p-6">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-zinc-400">
        <span data-lang="es">Formación</span>
        <span data-lang="en">Education</span>
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-300">
        <li>
          <span data-lang="es">2023-2025 · Grado Superior en Desarrollo de Aplicaciones Multiplataforma (IES Antonio Gala)</span>
          <span data-lang="en">2023-2025 · Higher VET in Multiplatform App Development (IES Antonio Gala)</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span data-lang="es">2020-2022 · Grado Superior en Automatizacion y Robotica (Colegio Salesiano San Luis Rey)</span>
          <span data-lang="en">2020-2022 · Higher VET in Automation and Robotics (Salesian School San Luis Rey)</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span data-lang="es">2018-2020 · Bachillerato de Ciencias (IES Antonio Gala)</span>
          <span data-lang="en">2018-2020 · Science Baccalaureate (IES Antonio Gala)</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/4 p-6">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-zinc-400">
        <span data-lang="es">Lo que he hecho</span>
        <span data-lang="en">What I have done</span>
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-300">
        <li>
          <span data-lang="es">2025-Actualidad · Desarrollador de software en Smart Fenix (lider SMART AGRO, IoT y datos).</span>
          <span data-lang="en">2025-Present · Software developer at Smart Fenix (SMART AGRO lead, IoT and data).</span>
        </li>
         <li>
          <span data-lang="es">2023-2025 · Hosteleria en Grupo MVP mientras estudiaba.</span>
          <span data-lang="en">2023-2025 · Hospitality at Grupo MVP while studying.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span data-lang="es">2022-2023 · Automatismos industriales: PLC, cuadros electricos y lineas automaticas (Cosentino, Valeo).</span>
          <span data-lang="en">2022-2023 · Industrial automation: PLCs, electrical panels and automated lines (Cosentino, Valeo).</span>
        </li>
          <li>
          <span data-lang="es">2023 · Auringis Automatismos.</span>
          <span data-lang="en">2023 · Auringis Automatismos.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span data-lang="es">2022 · Automatismos Brenton y Gomarsa Integracion (FCT).</span>
          <span data-lang="en">2022 · Automatismos Brenton and Gomarsa Integracion (internship).</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
